{"about_the_game":"Ball Bash is a fast-paced battle-racing party game that's easy to learn, while allowing a high skill ceiling for dedicated players. Share the fun with up to 4 players as you compete in several exciting game modes!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/Ability_Cards_Header.png?t=1737589626\" /><br>Cards are at the core of Ball Bash's hectic yet strategic gameplay. Use them to your advantage (or to your opponents' disadvantage!) in order to secure your victory.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/1newr.gif?t=1737589626\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/Characters_Header.png?t=1737589626\" /><br>Ball Bash features several charming ball-shaped characters, each with their own attributes and Card Decks. Play as an ancient jungle relic come to life, an escaped octopus in a spherical aquarium, or a yin-yang ball with a short temper.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/2newr.gif?t=1737589626\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/Game_Modes_Header.png?t=1737589626\" /><br>Ball Bash features multiple thrilling game modes that significantly alter the way you play, while keeping the core gameplay intact. Pass the bomb onto your friends before it explodes, race them to the finish line, or try to outrun a laser in the single-player Survival mode!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/extras/3newr.gif?t=1737589626\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737589626","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.s